References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

Use drm_crtc_mask() where appropriate.

Mostly performed with coccinelle:
@@
@@
- (1<<drm_crtc_index(
+ drm_crtc_mask(
  ...)
-  )

@@
@@
- 1<<drm_crtc_index(
+ drm_crtc_mask(
  ...)

@@
@@
- BIT(drm_crtc_index(
+ drm_crtc_mask(
  ...)
- )

